      "responsibilities": "<ul>\n<li>Design and deliver beautiful and crisp visual experiences across browsers and devices.</li>\n<li><span><span>Design and implement scalable back-end microservices and storage solutions for internal services and systems.<br></span></span></li>\n<li><span>Collaborate closely with cross-functional and product area teams in design, product, marketing, and engineering to create industry-leading experiences for our customers.<br></span></li>\n<li><span><span>Provide technical leadership and mentorship to your team members.<br></span></span></li>\n<li><span><div>Assist with migration efforts needed to implement a common user identity and management infrastructure across platforms (e.g., front-end and back-end).<br></div><div><br></div></span></li>\n</ul>",
