      "description": "<p>The Principal Engineer for Corporate Engineering (Corp Eng) will be a systems architect/liaison to different groups, and will bring together technologies across Corporate Engineering. You will engage with technical areas across Core and Google in representing Corp Eng focus and strategy, and connect Corp Eng to Core and company-wide priorities. </p>\n\n<p>You will support the Vice President of Corp Eng and partner closely with the Corp Eng leadership team to influence and define a technical roadmap for how Corp Eng evolves the architecture across proprietary builds and integrations of third-party tools. You will improve productivity by empowering Googlers with technology. </p><p>At Corp Eng, we build world-leading business solutions that scale a more helpful Google for everyone. As Google’s IT organization, we provide end-to-end solutions for organizations across Google. With an inclusive mindset, we deliver the right tools, platforms, and experiences for all Googlers as they create more helpful products and services for everyone. In the simplest terms, we are Google for Googlers.</p>",
