      "apply_url": "https://www.google.com/about/careers/applications/signin?jobId=CiUAL2FckdViuV0erOQhwEvR5v8W8jFAcF3lUbk8ahq9KXEGfiWDEjsAkXGnOyphaJ15AO-6ca1rc8KtPN4v7XDaUWGJn5xMa5sxj6MlYqCZRkWXDVn7x6a8wOkjbm2B2-feqQ%3D%3D_V2&jobTitle=Principal+Engineer&loc=US",
      "responsibilities": "<ul>\n<li><span><span>Understand the landscape of content moderation and anti-abuse systems within Google and outside, and ensure YouTube Trust and Safety platform is modern and industry leading.<br></span></span></li>\n<li><span><span>Provide technical vision and collaborate with cross-functional teams to set strategic direction from a technical perspective, and design and lead a multi-year technical roadmap.<br></span></span></li>\n<li><span><span>Provide domain expertise and engineering insight to guide early designs, accelerate project decision-making, maintain close oversight of technical execution, and proactively adjust course where necessary.<br></span></span></li>\n<li><span>Provide technical guidance to the team (e.g., review and approve technical designs, guide technical discussions, and project directions).<br></span></li>\n</ul>",
      "qualifications": "<p>Minimum qualifications:</p><ul>\n<li>Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, a related technical field, or equivalent practical experience.</li>\n<li>15 years of experience in software development in programming languages (e.g., C, C++, Java) to build distributed systems.<br></li>\n<li>Experience creating a vision for the future.<br></li>\n</ul><br><p>Preferred qualifications:</p><ul>\n<li>Experience in content moderation.<br></li>\n<li>Experience in cyber security.<br></li>\n<li>Experience working with full stack development and full release cycle.<br></li>\n<li>Experience driving a portfolio of concurrent engineering projects running the gamut from short-term critical feature launches to long-term research initiatives.<br></li>\n<li>Ability to promote product excellence and collaboration.</li>\n<li>Ability to think in a strategic manner to develop innovative platforms and execute a multi-year roadmap.<br></li>\n</ul>",
      "company_id": "companies/ad872500-709d-4a93-97e3-76be227f77a1",
