      "responsibilities": "<ul>\n<li>Create and lead innovative programs, software, and analytics that drive improvements to the availability, scalability, efficiency, and latency of Google Cloud Storage.\n</li>\n<li>Work in close partnership with product leads across multiple areas, on technologies to build fast, reliable, and durable production systems.\n</li>\n<li>Drive the technical guidance and strategy for Google Cloud Platform's (GCP) product portfolio to achieve infrastructure cost efficiencies balanced with our customers' need for highly available and performant services.</li>\n<li>Partner with Cloud Capacity, Capital Engineering, and the GCP Efficiency program to drive platform level features that improve cost efficiency across multiple services through improved surplus management, safety stock, fungible resource planning, and pool optimizations for non-allocated overheads. </li>\n<li>Lead the software engineering efforts by driving architecture selection, software design, execution, and operations.</li>\n</ul>",
