      "apply_url": "https://www.google.com/about/careers/applications/signin?jobId=CiUAL2FckcVxQ4t9RlVLmtlJrUHiL_Kysc0YiNDJbXo3dbTQY-mFEjsARYnzBZsurqLFI5TyXedyr-MLnUKalFSiQiI4szJ64Sh1_4jByYPDsxtoN5upAspoPj4Z_Ef9S1XMHA%3D%3D_V2&jobTitle=Principal+Engineer&loc=US",
      "responsibilities": "<ul>\n<li>Understand the landscape of rendering systems within Google and outside, and ensure the rendering stack for Search is modern.</li>\n<li>Drive the improvements needed in the rendering stack so Search developers are productive, including fundamental rethinking and rearchitecting of how rendering interfaces with the rest of the Search stack.</li>\n<li>Identify technological and experiential constructs that are required for that vision to be realized. Develop a roadmap that assembles the building blocks over time, including projects currently underway as well as new projects.</li>\n<li>Oversee and steer all the engineering projects in multiple locations as well as drive cross-functional engineering decisions across the sites to deliver an excellent offering.</li>\n<li>Provide domain expertise and engineering insight to guide early designs, accelerate project decision making and maintain close oversight of technical execution and proactively adjust course where necessary.</li>\n</ul>",
      "qualifications": "<p>Minimum qualifications:</p><ul>\n<li>Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or a related technical field, or equivalent practical experience</li>\n<li>15 years of experience in engineering</li>\n<li>Experience in software development using a general purpose programming language such as Java, JavaScript, Objective-C, or C++</li>\n<li>Experience in systems with reliability, scalability, and latency optimizations</li>\n</ul><br><p>Preferred qualifications:</p><ul>\n<li>Experience motivating others to act, creating a compelling vision for the future, communicating clearly, and using a collaborative leadership approach</li>\n<li>Experience in building UIs for consumer products on the web, Android, and iOS platforms</li>\n<li>Experience in the software development lifecycle process, including analysis and design, APIs, development tools and technologies, release and version control, contemporary testing methodologies, and deployment management</li>\n<li>Experience leading complex cross-functional engineering projects</li>\n<li>Experience in architecting, designing, and building large-scale distributed systems from scratch</li>\n<li>Ability to think strategically to develop innovative platform offerings, with a global mindset, and to operate across regional boundaries</li>\n</ul>",
