      "description": "<p>As a Principal Engineer and thought partner to the Senior Engineering Director for Search Rendering, you will lead the technical long-term strategy for rendering in Search, Google Assistant, and Discover products and working closely with our engineers to see it through, while setting high technical excellence in everything we do. You will be defining APIs and workflows for UI developers on these products, enabling them to build modern intuitive UIs as underlying products evolve through market forces, accelerating product iteration velocity and reducing their total cost of ownership.</p><p>Google is an engineering company at heart. We hire people with a broad set of technical skills who are ready to take on some of technology's greatest challenges and make an impact on users around the world. At Google, engineers not only revolutionize search, they routinely work on scalability and storage solutions, large-scale applications and entirely new platforms for developers around the world. From Google Ads to Chrome, Android to YouTube, social to local, Google engineers are changing the world one technological achievement after another.</p>",
